@api_base_url = https://localhost:7123

### Health Check
GET {{api_base_url}}/health

###

### Create a chat session with default model
POST {{api_base_url}}/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Create a chat session with specific model
POST {{api_base_url}}/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "sessionId": "my-custom-session-1"
}

###

### Send a simple message (update sessionId from response above)
# @name sendMessage
POST {{api_base_url}}/api/chat/my-custom-session-1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Hello! Can you explain what GitHub Copilot SDK is in one sentence?"
}

###

### Send a message asking for a calculation
POST {{api_base_url}}/api/chat/my-custom-session-1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "What is 25 * 4 + 100?"
}

###

### Get session history
GET {{api_base_url}}/api/chat/my-custom-session-1/history

###

### Delete a session (cleanup)
DELETE {{api_base_url}}/api/chat/my-custom-session-1

###
